WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.366 --> 00:00:06.000
Dr. Ye, you are here

2
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.133
Dr. Ye, thanks to your treatment

3
00:00:08.133 --> 00:00:10.466
I'm much better now

4
00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:15.000
Duan Lao, I'm here this time

5
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:16.133
There is a small favor

6
00:00:16.133 --> 00:00:18.466
Look how polite you are

7
00:00:18.533 --> 00:00:19.900
Feel free to ask

8
00:00:19.900 --> 00:00:22.300
Mr. Duan, you must know my background

9
00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:24.266
I want to ask you about my life experience.

10
00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:26.300
Why did you suddenly remember to ask this question?

11
00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:27.233
Is because

12
00:00:28.366 --> 00:00:30.800
Someone almost died because of my background

13
00:00:31.333 --> 00:00:34.266
I was sent to the mountains to study medicine with my master since I was a child

14
00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:37.166
My master only told me that my relatives were dead

15
00:00:37.166 --> 00:00:38.133
But never told me

16
00:00:38.133 --> 00:00:39.500
Why am I here now?

17
00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:41.500
I don't even know what kind of family I am

18
00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:43.366
Your master didn't tell you.

19
00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:44.933
He must have a point.

20
00:00:44.933 --> 00:00:46.133
I don't care.

21
00:00:46.133 --> 00:00:47.766
I just want to know my background

22
00:00:47.766 --> 00:00:49.066
If Duan Lao knew

23
00:00:49.166 --> 00:00:50.700
I hope Duan Lao will tell me

24
00:00:51.066 --> 00:00:52.466
How time flies!

25
00:00:52.466 --> 00:00:54.866
It's been more than 20 years

26
00:00:54.866 --> 00:00:56.166
It seems that you really know

27
00:00:56.166 --> 00:00:57.433
I know.

28
00:00:57.733 --> 00:00:59.666
But I can't tell you.

